OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCOP26: UK firms forced to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fplan for low-carbon future 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Most big UK firms and financial        
OL,6, institutions will be forced to show how
OL,7, they intend to hit climate change      
OL,8, targets under new Treasury rules.      
OL,10,FThey will have to detail how they will 
OL,11,Fadapt to a low-carbon future in order  
OL,12,Fto meet the UK's 2050 net-zero target. 
OL,14,FBut firms and their shareholders will  
OL,15,Fbe left to decide how their business   
OL,16,Fadapts to this transition, including   
OL,17,Fhow they plan to decarbonise the       
OL,18,Femissions they finance.                
OL,20,FFirms will publish the plans in 2023.  
